1月舉行會議，隨後為日本央行在12月加息打下基礎。外界因此關注，此次會面是否同樣將為未來的政策調整鋪路。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市早苗一直以倡導擴張性財政及貨幣政策而聞名。她在競選期間曾發表的言論，被市場解讀為強調日元疲弱對經濟的好處，也因此引發對匯率與利率政策方向的討論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，高市早苗有權提名今年日本央行9名成員理事會中的兩名空缺席位，這可能會影響央行未來的政策立場。目前，市場普遍預期日本央行在明年4月再次加息的可能性約為80%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>延伸閱讀：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:高市早苗勝選後將首次與日本央行行長舉行會議;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-033248511.html\"><strong>高市早苗勝選後將首次與日本央行行長舉行會議</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:避險資產不避險？市場重新評估美元、日元與瑞郎地位;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:c